title: Dual 1-6 (2008-2010) (Zuda) (Digital)
description:
English | CBR | 5 Issues

Dual #1-6
Publisher:  Zuda Comics
Publication Date:  June 2008 - 2010

Writer and Artist:  Michael Walton

Dual was an ongoing webcomic updating every Monday at Zuda.com.  When DC Comics closed Zuda Comics in October 2010, it brought the issues to Comixology.
Dual - Part 001 (incl. Prologue) (2008-2009) (CBR'ed by NW-DCP).cbr compiles parts 1-3.
Dual 001 (2010) (Zuda) (Digital) (ActionComics-DCP).cbr is part 1 with the cover.

At age ten, Bill Jensen and his "imaginary" friend, Yasu, inadvertently unlock a devastating power that kills three schoolmates. As adults, Bill and Yasu struggle to understand their extraordinary power, while encountering a cornucopia of supernatural creatures that secretly populate our world.
